# Docker Services

All containers use the `aboutme-` prefix for naming.

## Services

| Service | Container | Port |
|---------|-----------|------|
| PostgreSQL 16 | aboutme-postgres | 5432 |
| Redis 7 | aboutme-redis | 6379 |
| MinIO | aboutme-minio | 9000 (API), 9001 (Console) |

## Environment Variables

Default credentials follow the `aboutme` naming convention:
- Postgres: user=`aboutme`, password=`aboutme`, db=`aboutme`
- MinIO: user=`minioadmin`, password=`minioadmin`

All overridable via root `.env` file.

## Volumes

Named volumes: `aboutme_postgres_data`, `aboutme_redis_data`, `aboutme_minio_data`
